data.description: Secluded COUNTRY living at the core! This unique, massive, approximately 2371 SF, 4/2 rustic RANCH STYLE home, is sitting on approximately 11.5 unrestricted acres with a sizable pond, water well and all the room you need to spread your wings and enjoy life. The enormous covered front porch was built for the sole purpose of making many memories with family and friends. Sit under your carport, and gaze across the rolling terrain filled with majestic native trees and all sorts of wildlife roaming the property. The entire A/C unit was replaced in 2020 and has a quarterly pest control program. 2 water heaters. If you like to hunt and fish, go no further than your own backyard! Plenty of room for a garden, pool or outbuildings.  Situated in the HIGHLY sought after Big Sandy School District, you are only 20 minutes from Livingston and 20 minutes from the Naskila Casino. Call us today to schedule your own private showing. Let's make this HOME!
